Settings are preferences used to customize the VRChat experience. Menus for settings can be found in the Quick Menu, Main Menu, and Action Menu. They cover preferences for UI Elements, User Interface, Avatars, Your Avatar, Avatar Culling, Chatboxes, Display and Visual Adjustments, Comfort & Safety, Audio & Voice, Graphics, [[Special:MyLanguage/Mirrors|Mirrors]], [[Special:MyLanguage/Controls|Controls]], Tracking & IK, Accessibility, and Debugging.